    {
      "name": "Socket.IO Real-Time Updates",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Socket.IO Connection Guide",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/health",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "health"]
            },
            "description": "## Socket.IO Real-Time Updates\n\nPostman doesn't natively support Socket.IO. Use one of these methods:\n\n### Option 1: Browser Console (Recommended)\n1. Open browser DevTools (F12)\n2. Go to Console tab\n3. Run the code below:\n\n```javascript\n// Install socket.io-client first: <script src=\"https://cdn.socket.io/4.5.4/socket.io.min.js\"></script>\n\nconst socket = io('http://localhost:3000', {\n  query: {\n    token: 'YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE' // Get from Postman: {{access_token}}\n  }\n});\n\nsocket.on('connected', (data) => {\n  console.log('‚úÖ Connected to Socket.IO:', data);\n});\n\nsocket.on('orderUpdate', (data) => {\n  console.log('üì¶ Order Update:', data);\n  console.log('Order ID:', data.orderId);\n  console.log('Status:', data.orderStatus);\n  console.log('Payment Status:', data.paymentStatus);\n  console.log('Message:', data.message);\n});\n\nsocket.on('disconnect', () => {\n  console.log('‚ùå Disconnected from Socket.IO');\n});\n```\n\n### Option 2: Socket.IO Client Tool\nUse a tool like:\n- **Socket.IO Client** (Browser extension)\n- **Insomnia** (with Socket.IO plugin)\n- **Thunder Client** (VS Code extension)\n\n### Connection Details\n- **URL**: `http://localhost:3000`\n- **Authentication**: Pass JWT token in query params as `token`\n- **Events to listen**:\n  - `connected` - Connection confirmation\n  - `orderUpdate` - Order status/payment updates\n  - `pong` - Response to ping\n\n### Test Flow\n1. Connect to Socket.IO with your access token\n2. Create an order via API\n3. Complete payment (Stripe/PayPal)\n4. Receive real-time `orderUpdate` event\n\n### Example Event Payload\n```json\n{\n  \"orderId\": \"abc-123\",\n  \"paymentStatus\": \"PAID\",\n  \"orderStatus\": \"PROCESSING\",\n  \"message\": \"Payment successful! Your order is now processing.\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"2024-11-29T10:30:00.000Z\"\n}\n```"
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
